title: Martinibomb and the Coconut Monkeyrocket - Monster Beat Hallowee
description:
Martinibomb and the Coconut Monkeyrocket - Monster Beat Halloween Remix[AGENT]

Artist:Martinibomb and the Coconut Monkeyrocket 
Song:Monster Beat
Remix
Bitrate:160kbps

Happy Halloween 2014. Martinibomb and the Coconut Monkeyrocket join forces this scary season to bring you their spin on the theme of the Munsters television show! It arrives just in time for all the DJs and party hosts to work it into their ghoulish mixes.

Martinibomb made the creepy artwork for this single. He also created the cover for the Oddio Overplay theme compilation. Both Martinibomb and the Coconut Monkeyrocket shared fantastic tracks on that compilation you are sure to enjoy. Both are also musical artists on the Comfort Stand netlabel.
